item.title: Email marketing Stats for the ‘Cork Open Coffee Friday 5th February’ email
item.description: The last Cork Open Coffee reminder email to members was sent on Wednesday the 3rd of February at 9.50am. As promised, here are its stats: * Email sent to 157 email recipients. * Subject length: 6 Words (36 characters). * Open Rate: 29.6% * Bounce Rate: 3.2%. (Hard bounces, emails no longer exist) * Click Rate: 11.8% * Unsubscribe: 0 * New Subscriptions: 5 There were 7 links in the email.
